%s tlaīxkopīnkāyōtl kitekiwia īēkawīllōwikāwh pantayah inik kihkwilōs tlaēlilistli, mixtli, īwān achiyōtl īkwitlapān chipāwak xamixtli īwān ātl.
Inīn weli kihtlakoa miak tlachīwaltilistli īpan wasneki wastli īwān in ihkwāk kitekiwia 4K-pantayah.
options.graphics.fancy.tooltip:
Tlanesemīxnawalli tlaīxkopīnkāyōtl kitlanewiwilia tlachīwaltilistli īwān īpitsawakāyō miak wastli.
Tlaēlilistli, mixtli īwān achiyōtl weli ahnēsi in ihkwāk tikihttas īkwitlapān chipāwak xamixtli nosso ātl.
options.graphics.fast.tooltip:
Isiwhkak tlaīxkopīnkāyōtl kilokotskoa īaxkāwilis ihtōni ātl īwān sepayawitl. 
Tēskatikāyōpahyōtl ayoktlahsiwitilli ītlokpa miak xamixtli kēnwak iswatl.

Tikpantlasalihkeh motlamawisōltlahkwilōltōn ahtlahtlālilōni īka in %s tlaīxkopīnkāyōpehpenalistli
